        <abstract> 
<p>More praise for <hi rend="italic">Himalayan journals</hi>.</p> 
            <p>How remote was glacial action in Himalayas?</p>
            <p>Implies Himalayas were birthplace of many plants.</p> 
<p>Final volume of <hi rend="italic">Cirripedia</hi> to be printed in two or three months.</p> 
